trans-unit.source: Provides basic functionality for the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ContextMenuStrip"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder grunnleggende funksjonalitet for den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ContextMenuStrip"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Although ToolStripDropDownMenu and <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripDropDown"></xref> replace and add functionality to the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Menu"></xref> control of previous versions, <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Menu"></xref> is retained for both backward compatibility and future use if you choose.
trans-unit.target: Selv om ToolStripDropDownMenu og <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripDropDown"> </xref> erstatte og legge til funksjonalitet i <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Menu"> </xref> kontroll over tidligere versjoner <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Menu"> </xref> er beholdt for bakoverkompatibilitet og fremtidig bruk hvis du velger.

trans-unit.source: ToolStripDropDownMenu is the base class for <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ContextMenuStrip>, providing necessary painting and layout properties and methods.
trans-unit.target: ToolStripDropDownMenu er basisklasse for <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ContextMenuStrip>, gir nødvendig malingen fullføres og oppsettet egenskaper og metoder.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ContextMenuStrip>

trans-unit.source: The properties of this class that you are most likely to use directly are the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripDropDownMenu.ShowCheckMargin%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripDropDownMenu.ShowImageMargin%2A> properties, which determine whether the shortcut menu will be able to display a check mark, an image, or both.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapene til denne klassen som du er mest sannsynlig vil bruke direkte i <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripDropDownMenu.ShowCheckMargin%2A>og <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripDropDownMenu.ShowImageMargin%2A>Egenskaper, som bestemmer om hurtigmenyen skal kunne vise en hake og/eller et bilde.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripDropDownMenu.ShowImageMargin%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripDropDownMenu.ShowCheckMargin%2A>
